    example: "The Battle of Las Navas de Tolosa (1212) was a decisive turning point in the Reconquista, uniting the armies of Castile, Aragon, Navarre, and Portugal with papal support. The Christian victory broke the power of the Almohad Caliphate in Iberia. However, the Reconquista's legacy is complex: it also produced the forced conversion of Jews and Muslims and the establishment of the Spanish Inquisition in 1478.",
